      "paper_id": "paper",
      "text_span_id": null,
      "text": "The correlation graph shows that CS has strong positive relationships with 2 mg (78.8%), 1 mg (76.9%), and mc (72.1%), and moderate positive correlations with 8 mg (45%) and saliva (45.4%).",
